係越想知就越唔問佢<br />\n因為我知我仲介意 聽完自己會唔開心<br />\n所以一路等自己慢慢無咁介意 先開始去問佢以前嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油啊絲打 我都用左差唔多一年時間先唔介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打好勁好忍得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過佢同佢ex啲野係我自己發現既 一路睇感覺上就好似佢呃住我好多野咁<br />\n我會試下唔咁介意架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都有試過自己發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但人就係犯賤 個陣我係不斷睇佢ig以前啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就覺得佢好似愛ex多過我咁 打啲嘢又好sweet咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n越唔想睇佢嘅過去就越犯賤忍唔住去睇 <br />\n時間耐左慢慢就開始發現原來自己無以前咁在意佢啲ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到後尾再問佢先知其實原來唔係自己諗嘅咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n唔好俾大家嘅過去影響到 珍惜同佢一齊嘅每一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢都好努力氹返我去證明佢真係愛我同俾安全感我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你講得好岩啊絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要好好珍惜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家有時我會抽下佢水 佢又會抽返我水<br />\n唔緊要架 慢慢嚟 唔洗逼自己要一時之間就唔介意 時間真係幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63b43ddeba4bf1026c0d32b9baa25fcdca15f4e","tid":447471,"uid":32442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T01:54:30.000Z","msg":"睇落幾完美都好<br />\n散得咪即係唔work<br />\n盡量唔好問咁多la"},{"pid":"38b20ea85d3079646b1f0e9825a235b37f0b4f9e","tid":447471,"uid":99982,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T02:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主唔敢答佢個處係咪比呢條仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地奉旨要答你架 ?<br />\n係唔係處關你撚事咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i